title: What Happened, Brittany Murphy?
description:
Tig and Cheryl discuss "What Happened, Brittany Murphy?", a look back at the career and downfall of the gifted comedic actress. Did you know True Story has a LIVE streaming show on Nov 11? Tickets available now at loopedlive.com! *this episode spills beans* Get merch at podswag.com/truestory (tigandcheryltruestory@gmail.com)
